\cos^2 t + \sin^2 t = 1
\frac{a}{\cos^2 t} = \frac{b}{\sin^2 t}
t = \arctan \sqrt{\frac{b}{a}}
 \sqrt{(\cos^2 t + \sin^2 t)\left( \frac{a^2}{\cos^2 t} + \frac{b^2}{\sin^2 t} \right)} \geq (a+b). 
 D \leq \frac{|a^2 - b^2|}{a+b}  = |a-b|. 
